title: P-TECH praises Dunkirk Metal Products | News, Sports, Jobs - Evening Observer
content: P-TECH praises Dunkirk Metal Products | News, Sports, Jobs  Evening Observer
description: WNY P-TECH in Dunkirk has a foundation built upon recommendations from area manufacturing businesses. To recognize the industry it owes so much to the development of its students, P-TECH annually names a Business Partner of the Year. During a recent ceremony, WNY P-TECH named Dunkirk Metal Products as the 2021-22 Business Partner of the Year. [â€¦]
